                ["title"] = "侍者皎皎的商店上新",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-商业化-商店上新.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【启程系列礼箱】上架★</span></h2>\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QBYYdvH4XokVTRxwynxcGE71nSb\">【礼包上架时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HYBGdNhE5ou5zyxbeOscY3OWnMf\">2025年10月28日（UTC+8）开服后永久上架</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NLWrd1NrjoLEkdxSrfic56TTnMc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-R992deYBao2Vtlxt0hwc31NSnIg\">【礼包说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PE8Idd39CorluGxBQF0cAO15n5f\">该系列礼箱限购一次。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XiFzdMCh0oDS9Ax9oyIcm4LXnt2\">购买该系列礼包可获得「华彩沙漏」、「纯白沙漏」、「启航武器自选箱」、脸部装饰「圆框眼睛&middot;本色」、背部装饰「歌颂自由之风」、腰部装饰「阴阳玉」、头部装饰「心情&middot;彩虹」等道具。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WWcYddtXpoMlq5xoRJYctjQ6n7d\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PmxIdMwTtoK8X0xBCHicjw4Unjb\">【礼包内容】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PmxIdMwTtoK8X0xBCHicjw4Unjb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PmxIdMwTtoK8X0xBCHicjw4Unjb\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/OB【启程系列礼箱】上架.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<h2 class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PmxIdMwTtoK8X0xBCHicjw4Unjb\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒】上架★</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-商业化-【启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒】上架.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></span></p>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PmxIdMwTtoK8X0xBCHicjw4Unjb\">\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GLWLdOZ7AofEZexE5CbcFYnynWb\">【礼包上架时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XkBPdLAYgoEMsyxX7FIcZJAInTe\">2025年10月28日（UTC+8）开服后</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LusjdbVLAoX6E9xQe9fc8JbynVf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-S1zGdelgCoY3n5xNYFsclkPxngd\">【礼包售价】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PcgadLtgWoeyzcxlgwacrtkEn3g\">「月石晶胚」*1280</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Fk0sdGqbToN2xvxSXuwcDIkxnRd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Xt9Dd3cOCobiGqxHCTRc05wQnah\">【活动限时折扣】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JLSiddaYBoOm2PxrLFPcUqOKnKB\">活动期间首次购买，优惠价「月石晶胚」*780；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Xkm1dJaYoo4p7OxMv25cdN4ynfd\">二次购买，优惠价「月石晶胚」*980，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FUNDdbSVvoyTafxvFylcNqvgnJb\">活动结束后或购买2次后将恢复原价。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FUNDdbSVvoyTafxvFylcNqvgnJb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FUNDdbSVvoyTafxvFylcNqvgnJb\">\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-M9Ikd0QQsoImn7xaMs9cgWGbnFb\">【折扣时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TE40dCvr5oOiBcx1WImc4JqlnHd\">2025年10月28日开服后 ~ 2025年11月25日 04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TE40dCvr5oOiBcx1WImc4JqlnHd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TE40dCvr5oOiBcx1WImc4JqlnHd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TmCwd1tVLoYHHYxHJYacvxatnLn\">【启航自选形象奖励说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Shr7dVIu0oECXpxZY0GcnYvAnvc\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OTRTdjzwlotqb3xoko7cmn8anfe\">开启时可从贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zb3OdBpiRoO3i8x8Rgycu8XKnDg\">*如提前选择菲娜形象，可在后续获得角色菲娜时直接使用。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zb3OdBpiRoO3i8x8Rgycu8XKnDg\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FUNDdbSVvoyTafxvFylcNqvgnJb\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【狩月人形象礼箱&middot;星芒】上架★</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-商业化-【狩月人形象礼箱&middot;星芒】上架.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></span></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LZ8Idoi6FoTWAlxD5QCcElNzn2d\">【礼包上架时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CBH4dX5o6oPy2ZxuUP4ckP3Gnnf\">2025年10月28日（UTC+8）开服后</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FMBBdT6zIolIQex1AAtcJkmKnLb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NQyed1fxao4SLixu0w4cAYGvn5d\">【礼包售价】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NLxMdnlyJoMbdOxbVpjczOD3nwh\">128元</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y0JJd18AroBoIUxLuiNcY5slnUe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EHqWdHwcqoXSZDx0dICcORognMB\">【活动限时折扣】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EHqWdHwcqoXSZDx0dICcORognMB\">活动折扣期间 2025年10月28日开服后 ~ 2025年11月25日 05:00 优惠价6元，活动结束后将恢复原价。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EHqWdHwcqoXSZDx0dICcORognMB\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KUzRd9ZEuoVHP8xmKLAcSMvLn9b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qd4udsMutoNAslxJAWXcCPqFnNb\">【狩月人形象奖励说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CxSUdHiLno0h8Dx9neVcjdLnnWh\">购买礼包后，可同时获得狩月人两种形象的「星芒夜愿」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CxSUdHiLno0h8Dx9neVcjdLnnWh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h2 class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CxSUdHiLno0h8Dx9neVcjdLnnWh\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【万华限时礼箱】上架★</span></h2>\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZahQdFib7oSXeOxmxI1cPDuvnzd\">【礼包上架时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K1T1df4wUoRbMfxBR0bcSGywnOh\">2025年10月28日开服后 ~ 2025年12月22日 16:30（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ITwpdnRlBoiJlhxgr4mc5xdNnte\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ILZYd2zk9o3STpx3kFCcyZgjnYy\">【礼包说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VwBddx2otoDzgHxRrTscBHMwnBg\">活动期间【商店】将上架【夏夜万华系列礼箱】与【绮梦万华系列礼箱】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Kcg3doiLXo4JSrxvKqsc9fcLnpc\">购买后可获得「华彩沙漏&middot;限时」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B7k4dpQU8ovBBYxT2raceOrbn7d\">本期系列礼包中购买的「华彩沙漏&middot;限时」可用于在【夏梦纷飞集】中进行寻觅，【夏梦纷飞集】活动结束后将转换为「纯白沙漏」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B7k4dpQU8ovBBYxT2raceOrbn7d\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\">【礼包内容】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/【万华限时礼箱】上架.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1032\" height=\"325\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【外观形象装饰】新品上架★</span></strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JEMcdEywjoCf0txKFIycZyLxnLd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ug3SdckGpoG3OexoeHsc4TionVe\">【上架时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-C5GFdQ0ZmovzZWxqgx1c20I4n2e\">2025年10月28日（UTC+8）开服后</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ADrEdtdKboezDVx7e3wc2TaGndc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JfXadLyPxovUaoxMsvXcXvxanBI\">【售卖说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\">开服后以下形象将上架外观商店，可使用月石晶胚进行购买。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/OB【外观形象装饰】新品上架.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"983\" height=\"711\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">*更多装饰可前往【商店】-【外观】中查看。</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h2 class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【吟游诗集&middot;星芒颂Ⅰ】上架★</span></h2>\n<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-商业化-吟游诗集&middot;星芒颂.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E5ICdvW8KolVHbxwj4NcnncOnCg\">\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ia8YdU1uoohyp8xPQE0cdyJmnQd\"><strong>【开启时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LyufdUZfaoR7xMxMQx9cFMySnqd\">2025年10月28日开服后 ~ 2025年11月25日04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-STqVdmJXKonCXqxY6UFcpjptnFc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MMMvdy0GeoArg4x38wBcv7y5nqg\"><strong>【吟游诗集说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UyGzdkGhzo6JwMxxV5DccqHbnne\">&bull; 活动期间，狩月人可通过完成吟游诗集的见闻任务提升诗歌段落等级，领取丰厚奖励。每期吟游诗集开启后，将默认解锁平装诗集。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Fo2qd21lsoMWCHxT2TJccU2FnQg\">&bull; 解锁【精装诗集】并提升诗歌段落等级可获得「自选魔灵」、「月石」、「华彩沙漏」、「移转模块」、「武器移转模块」、「暮夜的履迹」、「委托手册」、「深红凝珠」等奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LWlbdcgknoTacIx3qMGcvrugnwc\">&bull; 解锁【典藏诗集】，除以上奖励外，可立即提升10级诗歌段落等级，还可额外获得「月石」*200、「委托手册&middot;三」*5以及「启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒」*1奖励！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XlZZdocnWobejfxoh95c2KXmnwc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Wo82dNbBEoFn8Ax2oEgcRM5NnRb\"><strong>【启航自选形象奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XkRHdKTY9oUkckxnkzFchofpnod\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VZd0dMCN8oDpYZxq1FXcZrGenfD\">开启时可从贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AvGfdlqesoDo53xnHK5c2YZXnI9\">*如提前选择菲娜形象，可在后续获得角色菲娜时直接使用。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LckZdX1OQopj03xPDSBcynTbnqd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QKfadPSJEoYd3zxAiuicNsEynaf\"><strong>【自选魔灵奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YV11d6IekoFeflxXnYFc3X2onEf\">吟游诗集达到30级并解锁【精装诗集】或【典藏诗集】，可从以下五星魔灵中自选召唤一只：「堇青艾尔芙」、「碧玺艾尔芙」、「玛瑙艾尔芙」、「紫晶艾尔芙」、「黑曜艾尔芙」、「欧泊艾尔芙」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-THILdC6gEo1y9LxtewwcRqyWnqs\">召唤魔灵后，可在【整备】-【魔灵】界面进行查看和装配。</div>\n<h2 class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-THILdC6gEo1y9LxtewwcRqyWnqs\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">★【侍者皎皎的月度订单】说明★</span></h2>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-THILdC6gEo1y9LxtewwcRqyWnqs\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-商业化-侍者皎皎的月度订单.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-THILdC6gEo1y9LxtewwcRqyWnqs\">\n<div data-page-id=\"V8n9dLwMGoioQnxHxzmc5D6Tneg\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FokydN4rqocuckxOd3JcgToVn5d\">&bull; 首次购买「侍者皎皎的月度订单」可立即获得当期专属头像框及300月石晶胚，同时订单签约生效时间延长30日。若连续购买签约多个订单，仅发放当前月份的限定头像框。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QKzmdQWxdoUqqfxtgC5ciarknUt\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，每日登录游戏可领取90月石，每日凌晨5点重置。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qf4PdLdjsoHhzExquEQcDK1anmZ\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，因为未登录游戏而未领取的月石，不会返还。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PrIVdugGNoiQSlx7Y8ecdxGPnPh\">&bull; 月度订单的签约生效时间小于90天时，才可继续购买并正常增加生效时长。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
