            [1] = {
                ["title"] = "版本维护更新说明",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/01-菲娜版本维护更新说明.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<p>亲爱的狩月人：<br>为了更好的游戏体验，《二重螺旋》计划将于2025年11月25日（星期二）<span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">09:45-10:45</span>进行停服更新维护，维护更新期间所有服务器将无法登录，请狩月人合理安排游戏时间。为保证您的游戏账号数据正常，请务必在本次维护前提前结束关卡。维护期间给各位狩月人带来的不便，我们深表歉意，感谢大家的支持与理解。</p>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-TEvldCjAKorN5rxocNNcT15FnFb\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong> ▍维护时间</strong></span></h3>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Uko2dJMP7oy7mRxHPwacj3BKnuf\">2025年11月25日（星期二）09:45-10:45</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QVB5dAaNgoDWcpx3sYRcxi5KnOc\"><strong>开服时间视维护进度有可能提前或推迟，还请留意公告通知。</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QVB5dAaNgoDWcpx3sYRcxi5KnOc\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\" old-record-id-DTaMdlQbsoVIP6x52Wpc1hqlnee\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-DTaMdlQbsoVIP6x52Wpc1hqlnee\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>▍新友相逢</strong></span></h3>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 188, 255);\">你与她相遇在小小的&ldquo;星空&rdquo;之下。<br>她以童话覆写旧伤，雪白的羽毛笔托起一个又一个柔软的幻想，乘着不羁的风儿，飞越城墙、荒原与寒夜。<br></span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 188, 255);\">因身体不佳而鲜少出门的菲娜，宛如童话故事中的夜莺一般，<br>在逼仄的小房间期待着天空、自由，以及，与亲人相聚的时刻。</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-菲娜-728.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"310\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QVB5dAaNgoDWcpx3sYRcxi5KnOc\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>「菲娜&middot;夜莺千夜谭」</strong></span>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AI11ddfdwoBLlpxfnIgchUtBnTy\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 属性：光属性</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GIq6dX7jFotVylx7Ck3cXhdfnDd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 武器精通：单手剑/突击枪</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GIq6dX7jFotVylx7Ck3cXhdfnDd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GIq6dX7jFotVylx7Ck3cXhdfnDd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SFb7dS4K6oyXcoxLrggcgQVtnrb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">【获取开放时间】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HwyudBpGcoBflRxGfWAcb0Kpnac\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日05:00（UTC+8）后长期开放。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-S4IudqgQBoCL0qx6tKfcz0CWnMS\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PhyLdbs1zovMS2xYlaacxqoHnyh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">【获取方式】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UyZQd3yE8ofztQxdomMcQc66nLy\" style=\"text-align: left;\">委托密函免费获得/商城购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WCUkdtzP3oyGEtxRlL6ct0Y9nub\" style=\"text-align: left;\">*「密函：菲娜」通过沉浸式戏剧玩法获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ERt6db2IOoHfKWxBXlacih3dn3f\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Snrqd8ZXxoTE4GxoXigcRQeQnrc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">【角色试用】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NTV8dki46oqHBqx2lhJc6DZqnRb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">更新后游戏内活动将开启「沙痕留迹」活动，狩月人可使用菲娜参与活动战斗关卡，完成关卡即可领取活动奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GveCdaGc7oUEKNxv1PVcAekEnDf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VZGcd62Vjos5P4xDpsIcUykQnsd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">【点滴&middot;光阴集】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VZGcd62Vjos5P4xDpsIcUykQnsd\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/03-菲娜邀约728.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"310\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 188, 255);\">「她将魔法的愿望寄于朋友。」</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAPkdgKIooK2NGxVgR3cgHM2nt4\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GbtUdGOfUo0AIrxYGzbcSp5jndh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 菲娜光阴集全剧情、全语音即将实装，狩月人可在获取菲娜后进入【休憩之所】点击【点滴】进入【光阴集】进行体验，完成任一阶段，可获得委托密函线索。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JAH2dRH66ozi3xxp33ccpc6lnlf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 解锁条件：完成全部任务：门后的秘密</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JAH2dRH66ozi3xxp33ccpc6lnlf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JAH2dRH66ozi3xxp33ccpc6lnlf\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-P02idt5eQoNywvxrd8TcILyhnud\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>&nbsp;▍新刃锋芒</strong></span></h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JAH2dRH66ozi3xxp33ccpc6lnlf\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/04-织梦的白羽-728.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"310\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JAH2dRH66ozi3xxp33ccpc6lnlf\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-Lvw3dTQLSoJ1BzxRdolcMVpinxe\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">「突击枪&middot;织梦的白羽」</span></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IyGwd4FvxomBdDxxSq2ct88snGd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Hz1Zd1R1Ho6kLPxKQGRcL1zdnid\" style=\"text-align: left;\">*「密函：织梦的白羽」通过沉浸式戏剧【观剧纪念】商店购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SiVRdfFsHowZLAxS3yqcIbDOnAg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 武器描述：我用雪白的羽笔编织了一个小小的笼子，把蛮荒的世界关了起来。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KrDJdL1k0oniTjxoDbxcMdQGnEh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 铸匠点评：即使是小小的鸟儿也有着大大的梦想。洁白羽翼下喷涌出的火焰，足以让每一个讨厌的坏家伙哭着求饶！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KrDJdL1k0oniTjxoDbxcMdQGnEh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JAH2dRH66ozi3xxp33ccpc6lnlf\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-EmEadH5Loo3ad7xYfercsb6XnBc\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong> ▍新活动开放</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 179, 245);\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/05-限时活动 -【夜莺飞往彩色的梦】菲娜角色剧情活动说明.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\">当一只小夜莺飞出巢穴，它会见到广阔的天空，掠过柔软的草地，却也注定会迎上冰冷的雨和狂暴的风。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 179, 245);\">但少女已决心不再退却，她将用魔法的画笔描绘彩色的梦，在这依然残酷的现实世界里，寻得一片永远如童话般温暖明亮的晴天。</span></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AB8XdIXKsoXZV2xICVjceTokn8f\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AB8XdIXKsoXZV2xICVjceTokn8f\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EaWudkCu1ojrNLxIFEncGthVnUe\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EaWudkCu1ojrNLxIFEncGthVnUe\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QLSrdKgrMoxG4MxYMVQcCTocntd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日10:00 ~ 2025年12月22日 17:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LMYrdNEx1o8p2CxgUCkcuTKNn5c\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-P0XNdNCjQo0gwsxkZ1PccsEanJd\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qjh6dT6WgoLrF2xsxQRcbpW2neb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">完成夜航篇第一章剧情【前往少女所说的宅邸】并开启【活动】功能。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B5FRdEtF5oV0XHxQ3JmcClLxn2n\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Nmm6dr6TeoztOFxNQMTcW3aLnIg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D1M0dFpauouQ89xmSNVcmNGFnbd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">「委托密函线索」、「深红凝珠」、「铜币」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SHw8dT6JIo7qMhxC2obcnSSYnth\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QLhBdiQxdoolMhxDNVxcyolGnKb\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JOyRdgdOwonMbdxM2qwcNQByn5e\" style=\"text-align: left;\">活动开启后，会随时间进度逐渐开启4个不同副本。</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BYkTd9MGwoOHz4xtf9ecYfC5nAf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【告别旧日的洞窟】开启时间：2025年11月25日10:00（UTC+8）</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KUyvdCeKjo3HT8xpKvUctfkbnZg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【穿行记忆的迷宫】开启时间：2025年11月26日05:00（UTC+8）</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TTjcdlMxJoHd9ExDsNEcARd0nSe\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【渡越荆棘的河谷】开启时间：2025年11月27日05:00（UTC+8）</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AxesdNpaDoz9rCxgDONclqT2nrf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【踏上芬芳的原野】开启时间：2025年11月28日05:00（UTC+8）</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RDlDdX0pgoeItrxpUWHcMjwBnVf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">在副本中使用染料，为世界上色，完成故事。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TDXrdgnf8oIqUwxiVQjc1JggnSb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">活动期间在副本内收集「白鸟之羽」，领取限时活动奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TqLidxe6FoW4SHxp8DRcKOvAnXq\" style=\"text-align: left;\">活动结束后副本转为常驻副本，但无法通过收集「白鸟之羽」获取限时的活动奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TqLidxe6FoW4SHxp8DRcKOvAnXq\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TqLidxe6FoW4SHxp8DRcKOvAnXq\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/06-限时活动 -【夜莺来信】累计签到领取「华彩沙漏」.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TqLidxe6FoW4SHxp8DRcKOvAnXq\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UIwcdjpD3ozYDXx8hf5c18JZnLo\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UIwcdjpD3ozYDXx8hf5c18JZnLo\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PFZodLpMIo2UuOxtEsjc928pndh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日10:00 ~ 2025年12月22日 17:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Qr4yd03tcoXSakxKoIdcn8GWnSb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OIfwdIbvXoTyUDxLKAZcD1Hwnne\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WEg5d6pSJoFTd1xHCGfcU92onvb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">完成夜航篇第一章剧情【前往少女所说的宅邸】并开启【活动】功能</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y7DRdtjSQobS7Nx1om6crdQzn6c\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PJqldH9LWoHuY8xr1rccBrmOneg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GJdLdccu4ob6egxfhlIcf9oHnoc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">「华彩沙漏」*10</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-V3PtdZmxTobIWxxKg3Gcw0afnkf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RVfIdDAYYoNtjRxVeVScid0Mnef\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Jv92d5o9cobSUExQPv3cfHYUnpc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 活动开启期间，狩月人累计登录七天即可解锁全部奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XSjddADLuoOXdsxght1cBkvInNh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 每日登录游戏，即可在活动界面领取当日奖励内容。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B7bZd4T43oXWzSxcjuLc0o4JnFf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 当日已解锁但未领取的奖励将在活动页面保留，可在活动期间的任何时间领取。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B7bZd4T43oXWzSxcjuLc0o4JnFf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B7bZd4T43oXWzSxcjuLc0o4JnFf\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/07-限时活动 -【沉浸式戏剧】参演热映剧目，领取菲娜委托密函！.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-B7bZd4T43oXWzSxcjuLc0o4JnFf\">\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YcRydaaFeoRc8cxnSfxcqmk2nCh\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 188, 255);\">沉浸式戏剧已开启，踏上舞台，演绎属于你的剧目。</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Xvp4drY5johXA0x3ELscMB21nFK\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HcXBdNz6WoNdC8xdDFmcjxqKn1D\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【开启条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UmXFdR1fRoImRsxXU4kcGtfmnBc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">完成泊暮篇剧情【审判日】与剧情任务【全新戏剧】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-HSFJda4Fdo5mKHxwMRzcyDDunsg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VfX9dRKL6oQcZFx8aVucvIoHnSf\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【本期时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UFTddMdXrolrQJxw1zKcxewwnJf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日 05:00 ~ 2025年12月23日 04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CQBodSTPAoVfRMxwBARcnOpLnln\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-US8PdAQwPozKbWxLltocxfSRnJd\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【本期奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LIbHdUUtroVitIx7UPDcNmVhnLg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 179, 245);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」</strong></span>「委托密函线索」、「养成材料」、「魔之楔」、「铜币」等。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BG9Odua50oRWcexGvUJcLvXTnnd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DEpldoANdomMsjxPdjxcHkFQnWh\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【限时奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q7iOdJlWMozIzzx8k4RcCLcCn7g\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 179, 245);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」</strong></span>为本期限时奖励，本期结束后替换为新角色/武器的委托密函。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U5D4dFlCZoGqRyxL2qjczSqZnsc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">「密函：菲娜」可通过达成本期【热映剧目】与【不朽剧目】的星级获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KB17dsNfIovHOXx5asScVx61nIg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">「密函：织梦的白羽」可在【观剧纪念】商店中使用「剧目票根」兑换获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SqsvdonYmok4YjxsoBoclkDJnyh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">在本期【沉浸式戏剧】结束后，「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」将替换加入【梦魇残声】每周挑战的挑战奖励中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GadeduYI6oq3vrxKCE2c6KSYnZc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ULIlddeeaocRArxnieSc6ZVInWg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【玩法说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U1rdd3Nhfo3AnjxP5VkcZgTOnnb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 沉浸式戏剧分为【经典剧目】、【热映剧目】与【不朽剧目】三部分。需完成前一剧目，才能解锁下一剧目。其中【热映剧目】和【不朽剧目】会随版本更新轮换，【不朽剧目】开放永续关卡，满足条件即可无限挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BFHtdpbHWoqx1TxqOcVc6Ul1n4e\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 在限定时间内击败关卡内所有敌人即算完成挑战，在每个剧目下，伴随通关都将获得一定的星数和「票根」，狩月人可在奖励列表领取星数奖励，并在观剧纪念商店兑换心仪的物品。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SZ6adM47rop8FDx43eSc9nLFnLc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 【经典剧目】与【热映剧目】包含【勇者征程】与【勇者归途】两轮战斗，需分别使用不同的角色配队出战，最终以两轮战斗获得的总星数结算奖励。不朽剧目仅有【勇者征程】一轮战斗。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TvU4dNztuoBlsHxI2BVc8us7neg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 每轮战斗分为5个房间，需逐层推进。通关当前层【勇者征程】【勇者归途】两轮的全部房间后，才可解锁下一幕关卡。超时或未击败当前房间的目标，都将无法进入下一房间。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PLATdMAONouG2OxoikBconLSntc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 所有关卡附带【舞台伴奏】效果，提供战斗中增益/减益Buff，需根据效果调整策略。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UDpbduw0nocPCwx6BIPcguUqnnh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ASA7dQ2KjoxwXGx7Uq6cKuNjnOc\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【舞台伴奏轮换说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-En4zdj6gvonmwRxH0W3cuQhAnBb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">随着本次沉浸式戏剧更新，剧目中的【舞台伴奏】与【推荐属性】也会一同进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E7USdvmNqoUk5QxX1pDckX7Ungb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">本期推荐属性：<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\">风属性</span>、<span style=\"color: rgb(136, 16, 216);\">暗属性</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Vy19dXB69o89mjxQyhxcZKXWnsf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">本期【舞台伴奏】将会轮换一批新的&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;，以下为【不朽剧目】中部分&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;：</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GgGOdX6eDofddsx8blXc4BzJneh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【抉择变奏：风与暗之歌】：敌方单位受到的风属性及暗属性伤害提高400%，受到的其他伤害降低50%。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KoPPdjrJ3o1hdixkEAIcNS0wnLf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【激昂行板：追寻魔力的飞鸟】：友方单位造成武器伤害时，目标每带有1个属性额外触发效果，此次伤害的暴击提高20%，最多叠加4次。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WH38dDb5fooLnGxLOEgcmewQn8c\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【活跃急板：失控档案】：友方单位每累计消耗15神智时，获得1层技能威力提高20.0%，持续15秒，最多叠加5层，满层时受到伤害不会产生僵直。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-G28bd31Z2oefDnx9l0EcZGEYnJP\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>【协调柔板：灵魂内视】：友方单位暴击伤害降低50.0%，造成技能伤害时有100%概率触发属性额外效果。</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote class=\" old-record-id-M9qedsc36oCEKKxcq8pckUA4n8e\" data-type=\"quote_container\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y6gVdfwMlomghCxpMTNcOXWJnGd\"><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 188, 255);\">更多【舞台伴奏】可在版本更新后进入游戏内查看。</span></div>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y6gVdfwMlomghCxpMTNcOXWJnGd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-CXfPdyAu2olvmYxqfgEcFmYMn0g\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/08-菲娜委托密函轮换说明.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JcCldWwOooYuJ8xj1WLca8Pmn5t\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JcCldWwOooYuJ8xj1WLca8Pmn5t\" style=\"text-align: left;\">委托密函将于2025年11月25日 更新后进行轮换，以下为轮换规则。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Y0exd13RQoJQfJxuiUFcwFG7nQb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日 05:00（UTC+8）：</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FDN8d3AqMoNaVKx9o9rc0lB7ned\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 188, 255);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」</strong></span><strong>将替换</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\"><strong>「密函：赛琪」「密函：希冀的丰稔」</strong></span>进入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中。</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-G6DPdSzptoOoI1xZE2wcrv56nFf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日版本更新后：</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zzy1dTaVwoQZxyxkTZGc1ynNn1d\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\"><strong>「密函：赛琪」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：塔比瑟」</span>加入梦魇残声【西比尔】挑战奖励中。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Env4dKKskon7xZxAhkWcnXN8nPf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\"><strong>「密函：希冀的丰稔」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：孤子的缚锁」</span>加入梦魇残声【西比尔】挑战奖励中。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-C3ufdmsIGo0PsKxdVXmcWciFnkc\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：塔比瑟」</span>与<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：孤子的缚锁」</span>将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VH1ydeQNdojAdQxttgycPSPQnwh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">特别提醒：本次梦魇残声奖励轮换调整时间为2025年11月25日10:00（UTC+8）（周二），更新后<strong>不会重置</strong>梦魇残声周奖励次数，若想获取<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\"><strong>「密函：赛琪」「密函：希冀的丰稔」</strong></span>的狩月人，可以将奖励次数留置更新后进行挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VH1ydeQNdojAdQxttgycPSPQnwh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VH1ydeQNdojAdQxttgycPSPQnwh\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/09-限时任务 -【剧情前置】异乡来客.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VH1ydeQNdojAdQxttgycPSPQnwh\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q8AQdjnDho3JYpxKBp4cZ9Bbnhb\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RZfVdf6hioTNSRxJQEsc8gZynGc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年12月08日 10:00 ~ 2025年12月23日 04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QEBVdFrd0oZrkCxMgnncWgSrnHb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DVXFdmnr3okJ9Cx98xWcQzSangb\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JgaldAwO0oXxTpxSae5cNvmCnTD\" style=\"text-align: left;\">完成剧情任务「夜航篇&middot;致无名者的安魂曲」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-H9M1dCNjAotj4fxzOkQcoTVNnNf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-O92KdqR8fonTdQx9IGccSVKvnJd\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Br34dn5KgoXfWxxUF52cKhS2nhf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">「暮夜的履迹」、「委托密函线索」、「深红凝珠」、「铜币」、「战斗旋律」、「武器说明书」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JFyFd5iEPobBwyxD7MDcQh6Bndd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VHqidF286oFlI8xOcy5cQdhJnyb\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【活动说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EfvvdevLBoh4JixanSscm4kknwe\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 在活动解锁后，狩月人可前往活动界面接取止流的委托任务，完成委托可获得暮夜的履迹、委托密函线索等奖励，使用代币可在商店兑换丰厚奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RIU1dz5E2oMTNHxfphCctZ9Dnch\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 活动持续期间，每日将发布两个委托，狩月人完成前一日的全部委托后，才可解锁并接取第二日的委托。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RIU1dz5E2oMTNHxfphCctZ9Dnch\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RIU1dz5E2oMTNHxfphCctZ9Dnch\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/10-商业化-商店上新.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RIU1dz5E2oMTNHxfphCctZ9Dnch\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-BMOfdxPz5oMcTVxrYrNcZQkEnnd\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>全新配色足迹特效、光晕上架棱镜商店</strong></span></h4>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FvxodE7GWo0yBoxpoROcegBJnsg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【上架时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UotpdOBLwo82mDxERppcncEOnAE\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日 10:00</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QXnKdV2MvodlWqxqflvcX9GmnQO\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OxJidbFN0oNLCQx8Y7Jc3RY5nEg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【售卖说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Etz1d35oVol6A4xbbKWcqucznmo\" style=\"text-align: left;\">在本次更新后，棱镜商店将上新以下内容：</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RD2AdKC56olhTqxeXuDcD9dwnMg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>光晕：</strong>「夏夜邀约&middot;锈红」「夏夜邀约&middot;涅白」「夏夜邀约&middot;墨玉」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MmHgdtpdeosFY0xTpbkcsBMAngf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>足迹特效</strong>：「摇曳轨迹&middot;锈红」「摇曳轨迹&middot;涅白」「摇曳轨迹&middot;墨玉」</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W9O9dBGRioMnCqxhkXvcEoTonvd\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YN4sdnC8VoQpFIx1x8fcZUtNnmg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">【其他说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X9ecdwOdToNbPLxYfWPc6et6nMb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">由于本次为棱镜商店首次上新，且公告时间与商店更新间隔较短，为优化各位狩月人的游戏体验，我们将在版本更新后，通过游戏内邮件为此前兑换过原色版本「夏夜邀约」或原色版本「摇曳轨迹」的狩月人，返还其对应消耗的「虹色棱镜」。返还邮件预计在版本更新一周内陆续送达。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JibrdN4jZojdLnx9wFUcCCTZngh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">举例说明：如某狩月人在11月25日前兑换了原色版本「夏夜邀约」与「摇曳轨迹」，版本更新后将收到虹色棱镜*12的返还邮件。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">未来，棱镜商店将根据大家的反馈持续扩充与上新，每次上新前均会提前发布公告，敬请留意。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-LNG7do76ToBBWQxyAoKcNSn1nbe\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>【外观形象装饰】新品上架</strong></span></h4>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZBctdnwZvoExrTxdT61c0PG7nvg\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【上架时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E9HMdXrztoUxtRxIXOkcP0Axn7d\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日 10:00</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LNhldyJcYoL1yvxq3sDcEQaLnAg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NfIldKoNgo5F0dxifIVc0jkKnZf\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【售卖说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ThD3dnV1sovpf7xllEoc8u1FnUh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">在本次更新后，外观商店将上新以下内容</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YZyhdtRX9oypn8xqoMmctFacnyh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>武器形象：</strong>「重剑-群星之焰」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Z2gvdC8U8owuWWxEPdJc0o23nWb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>腰部配饰：</strong>「玩偶的童话」「玩偶的童话&middot;墨玉」「玩偶的童话&middot;白樱」「玩偶的童话&middot;晴蓝」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XRIydLzF2ot1CaxN1agcjhXtnvg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>头部配饰：</strong>「梦中的夜莺」「梦中的夜莺&middot;涅白」「梦中的夜莺&middot;白樱」「梦中的夜莺&middot;杏黄」「日冕光轮」「心情&middot;下雨」「心情&middot;下雪」「心情&middot;气泡」「心情&middot;肯定」「心情&middot;惊叹」「心情&middot;迷惑」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-M4jkdoGJWoTC7vxy3V8cXMVJnof\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>背部配饰：</strong>「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;锈红」「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;杏黄」「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;白樱」「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;墨玉」</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-RR3zd7vHaoNoF0xc7lXcPiyTnrM\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/11-吟游诗集2 728x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></h4>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-RR3zd7vHaoNoF0xc7lXcPiyTnrM\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>【吟游诗集&middot;星芒颂II】上架</strong></span></h4>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PWP3dZazDoois4xe9rycRjTEneb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">※ 解锁【典藏诗集】即可获得「启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒」*1!</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zs4ldI231onXqDxzS8Vcb9Benid\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JJqsd5M9ToxVPzxMgMVcFYiinOe\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【开启时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JfaldzfLPoHlqSx6R8CcamyEnih\" style=\"text-align: left;\">2025年11月25日 05:00 ~ 2025年12月23日04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JTGEdkbdZoIY8lxG9guclWUrnkc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-A6CRdLKUcoamcJxLAqWc8c0lnGh\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【吟游诗集说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TCf5dNms3oNVqKxhjUXcKS1Hndb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 活动期间，狩月人可通过完成吟游诗集的见闻任务提升诗歌段落等级，领取丰厚奖励。每期吟游诗集开启后，将默认解锁平装诗集。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VJcrdnrVsoTvpuxqPNgcOUFsnng\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 解锁【精装诗集】并提升诗歌段落等级可获得「自选魔灵」、「月石」、「华彩沙漏」、「移转模块」、「武器移转模块」、「暮夜的履迹」、「委托手册」、「深红凝珠」等奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZJnhdnViiojezgxRb14cza3lnek\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 解锁【典藏诗集】，除以上奖励外，可立即提升10级诗歌段落等级，还可额外获得「月石」*200、「委托手册&middot;三」*5以及「启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒」*1奖励！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PvZrdICdAo5fOExMmfscAMPbnyg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Vowsd5Halo2yMsxuzQHcDhZdnSh\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【启航自选形象奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QNtEd0UYPopb0rx9ILGcOmLBnQe\" style=\"text-align: left;\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SUUQd3coEovlErx1AK3cm4cbncg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">开启时可从贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JQF7dliQQo9UEbxgjMXcrQwdncf\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K9ZhdBzI9oit1VxAgxdcuwfwnPf\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>【自选魔灵奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YasadQ4Xvoqja1xHfO4cI7dUnhg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">吟游诗集达到30级并解锁【精装诗集】或【典藏诗集】，可从以下五星魔灵中自选召唤一只：「堇青艾尔芙」、「碧玺艾尔芙」、「玛瑙艾尔芙」、「紫晶艾尔芙」、「黑曜艾尔芙」、「欧泊艾尔芙」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\" style=\"text-align: left;\">召唤魔灵后，可在【整备】-【魔灵】界面进行查看和装配。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/12-月卡头像框-菲娜.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-JyRddM0t8oTInDxvmZ1c8O7rn5c\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">【侍者皎皎的月度订单】说明</span></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JBzbd3aRNozOwox3z3Bcdl9nn6g\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 首次购买「侍者皎皎的月度订单」可立即获得当期专属头像框、300月石晶胚、1本委托手册&middot;四，同时订单签约生效时间延长30日。若连续购买签约多个订单，仅发放当前月份的限定头像框。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-To9idhqVropKOfxcAmOcgL5KnOY\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，每日登录游戏可领取90月石，1本委托手册&middot;二，每日凌晨5点重置。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X50UdF7POoGAhbxhnXKcqoGgn5c\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，因为未登录游戏而未领取的月石、委托手册，不会返还。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EocodPXhVojMiyxzjSOcp62MnNc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; 月度订单的签约生效时间小于90天时，才可继续购买并正常增加生效时长。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EocodPXhVojMiyxzjSOcp62MnNc\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EocodPXhVojMiyxzjSOcp62MnNc\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-Se9udxLvPoPFJxxcWf8crQbJnDh\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong> ▍补偿内容</strong></span></h3>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GWHudvfxroATi0xIOaJc9c73nvg\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 维护更新补偿：「委托手册&middot;二」*5</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NyM7dVOrdozYUdxXb5QcoY4Enxt\" style=\"text-align: left;\">✦ 领取条件：解锁【邮件】功能，邮件领取有效时间至2025年12月02日23:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WjFkdi4ndoShXyxaVlSczrLsncb\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Cxa8dyKvEoHc4XxKRlDcJlAinxh\" style=\"text-align: left;\">《二重螺旋》运营团队</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
