            [1] = {
                ["title"] = "「夏梦纷飞集」活动限定万华开启！",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/02-商业化-夏梦纷飞集.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"WHpmdJo0XoYcGtxZgbVcPu2Yn4b\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E3uBdIMPfob8ihxP0J5cfFrVnSc\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Vz7fdldC7o20WXx8KbrcCWtPnrf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Shdkd8Y8noWpwixaMpjcFLuun6g\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Vz7fdldC7o20WXx8KbrcCWtPnrf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Shdkd8Y8noWpwixaMpjcFLuun6g\"><strong>【活动时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GfCzdJjrJo95ADx6Lugc4tmLnYf\">\n<div data-page-id=\"WL6Pd3HJcoy8aKxKlMgcJv8Uned\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OXr3dOjgQoBWNUxot8ZcpSHSnpc\">2025年10月28日开服后 ~ 2025年12月22日 17:00（UTC+8）</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OBehdfz60oLo2OxmWVuceON2nqc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-G1frdbrB4oo9ypx2pvTcXSnCnKO\"><strong>【开放条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UreMdvbb4omI6XxbkDEcz2Uqn22\">完成夜航篇第一章剧情【前往少女所说的宅邸】并开启【万华】功能。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AAaXd3C38oKyQ3x4r4Pc54LonUb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E6RFdK6NwoL89KxrEyac08MxnWc\"><strong>【寻觅说明】</strong></div>\n<div data-page-id=\"WL6Pd3HJcoy8aKxKlMgcJv8Uned\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SZywdCCJOoxUOsxBG4cc3C66nig\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>参与本期寻觅有概率获得「赛琪-梦中的舞会」「虹色棱镜」等形象与道具。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q75Rd0kKMoelVcxcpRrcStLRn0e\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>「虹色棱镜」可在本期【限时兑换】中兑换本期【夏梦纷飞集】系列限定外观。本期系列包含以下内容：角色形象、武器形象、角色衣饰、武器装饰、展示动作。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-D21VdHv5MofFNaxDvUFcPtBTnxb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>本期限定形象「赛琪-梦中的舞会」仅可在【夏梦纷飞集】与「限时兑换」中获得，【夏梦纷飞集】活动结束后，在「限时兑换」中仍会存在一段时间，活动时间结束后暂无获取途径。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZrSQdnf28oYmmPxpc2IcYWG6n9f\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>活动期间本期限定形象「赛琪-梦中的舞会」将开启【绮夜入梦】时装试玩活动，完成试用关卡即可领取奖励。</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LRjsdZXaXo56XQx93S5cRW1Vn7d\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div>在本期【夏梦纷飞集】累计寻觅一定次数之后，可以在活动页面领取「华彩沙漏&middot;限时」道具。「华彩沙漏&middot;限时」可用于在【夏梦纷飞集】中进行寻觅，【夏梦纷飞集】活动结束后将转换为「纯白沙漏」。</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<blockquote class=\" old-record-id-SMW6dmSvlojC76xH4jGcAi8WnOg\" data-type=\"quote_container\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Kav9dTvJvo0JifxQGHUcKQBHn1c\">更多活动详细内容，请前往游戏内「万华」界面查看。</div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
