        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["title"] = "【沉浸式戏剧】参演热映剧目，领取菲娜委托密函！",
                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"WvWidHb1YodrgOxMKTFctEHLnlc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h2 class=\"heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-LHpNd665BosmaFxPlaOchwWsnS7\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/01-限时活动 -【沉浸式戏剧】参演热映剧目，领取菲娜委托密函！.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></h2>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KAxidplntob9zuxo1Bncil68ngh\">沉浸式戏剧已开启，踏上舞台，演绎属于你的剧目。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CoYDd42lpov5NyxgZayc9Rw1nxx\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UQqUdl5htoJ7ydxwQ9bcvyrqnpg\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DyMfdCf5gowZENxQVgTcN9gvnOc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnkSgCDPKc4ASlPOAD3bWmff\"><strong>【开启条件】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn7MUrosn6zC57egnelWvzrg\">完成泊暮篇剧情【审判日】与剧情任务【全新戏剧】。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn28IgXOs5qMOoPiBK05Yoqb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQO3CgN0aCdJZAT9fFJ6mUp\"><strong>【本期时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZLvFe6RxiD11D83wgQMNeg\">2025年11月25日 05:00 ~ 2025年12月23日 04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n</div>\n）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QTPZdlfA3ojRd5xg7U6cRvbdnUe\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-J0EKdfkIrommiAxqntcceFAknkc\"><strong>【本期奖励内容】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZrZbdXQSgookOKxjbg2cqQOznDb\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DyMfdCf5gowZENxQVgTcN9gvnOc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnXSJkJ91OxdA2JGbDcbc9gf\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 179, 245);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」</strong></span>「委托密函线索」、「养成材料」、「魔之楔」、「铜币」等。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NqoAd74yxoYNfjxwAnxcOZXYn3d\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QNM1dxwHuofkHExgBRhcjMsmnye\"><strong>【限时奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-U9g1dF0eToF8Yrxipr9cCmgQnNe\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DyMfdCf5gowZENxQVgTcN9gvnOc\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnjLZwuAAP1CAOzdKp8E3zub\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 179, 245);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」</strong></span>为本期限时奖励，本期结束后替换为新角色/武器的委托密函。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnCPgbIcfpHKMeTZblH3uI0w\">「密函：菲娜」可通过达成本期【热映剧目】与【不朽剧目】的星级获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn9s3xm9khCnywV0fmAJjepd\">「密函：织梦的白羽」可在【观剧纪念】商店中使用「剧目票根」兑换获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnaDJQE1Lf8uOfRFBS2Pht2b\">在本期【沉浸式戏剧】结束后，「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」将替换加入【梦魇残声】每周挑战的挑战奖励中。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Tck9dkVnZoycYBxlSM6ccEo9n9g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VnkwdxsNHoF7hixObG7c1z9fnj1\"><strong>【玩法说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OE2GdkyM3omHvsxXJLwctdnjnsd\">&bull; 沉浸式戏剧分为【经典剧目】、【热映剧目】与【不朽剧目】三部分。需完成前一剧目，才能解锁下一剧目。其中【热映剧目】和【不朽剧目】会随版本更新轮换，【不朽剧目】开放永续关卡，满足条件即可无限挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SROpdKtbvoHKd3xxYDBcxFrUnKc\">&bull; 在限定时间内击败关卡内所有敌人即算完成挑战，在每个剧目下，伴随通关都将获得一定的星数和「票根」，狩月人可在奖励列表领取星数奖励，并在观剧纪念商店兑换心仪的物品。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GSxpd33idotAgFxQq9Hc2km2n4e\">&bull; 【经典剧目】与【热映剧目】包含【勇者征程】与【勇者归途】两轮战斗，需分别使用不同的角色配队出战，最终以两轮战斗获得的总星数结算奖励。不朽剧目仅有【勇者征程】一轮战斗。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XyGGdeq2MokyBDxSL0FcAmU9nKe\">&bull; 每轮战斗分为5个房间，需逐层推进。通关当前层【勇者征程】【勇者归途】两轮的全部房间后，才可解锁下一幕关卡。超时或未击败当前房间的目标，都将无法进入下一房间。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Lcf3dubnmoWKoVxtBM9c2iFynNb\">&bull; 所有关卡附带【舞台伴奏】效果，提供战斗中增益/减益Buff，需根据效果调整策略。</div>\n</div>",
